<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="550" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,151,392]" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,223,248]" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="Zheng, 1981" authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1981" box="[330,624,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Flatovertex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cyaneitibialis">
<emphasis box="[330,624,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Flatovertex cyaneitibialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described based on the 
<typeStatus box="[990,1049,224,248]" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">types</typeStatus>
from Leishan County, Guizhou Province, 
<collectingCountry box="[267,334,260,285]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">China</collectingCountry>
(Zhang &amp; Han, 
<number box="[528,589,260,284]" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" value="2010.0">2010</number>
). Since 
<taxonomicName authority="Zheng, 1981" authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1981" box="[681,810,260,285]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Flatovertex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[681,810,260,285]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Flatovertex</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was synonymized with 
<taxonomicName box="[1091,1231,261,284]" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Pternoscirta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1091,1231,261,284]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Pternoscirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, it was compared with all 
<taxonomicName box="[257,397,297,320]" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Pternoscirta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[257,397,297,320]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Pternoscirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species. As a result, we found that 
<taxonomicName authority="Zheng, 1981" authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1981" box="[851,1145,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Flatovertex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cyaneitibialis">
<emphasis box="[851,1145,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Flatovertex cyaneitibialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
completely agreed with 
<taxonomicName box="[151,421,332,357]" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Pternoscirta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="caliginosa">
<emphasis box="[151,421,332,357]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Pternoscirta caliginosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
morphologically. Therefore, we propose 
<taxonomicName authority="Zheng, 1981" authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1981" box="[916,1210,332,357]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Flatovertex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cyaneitibialis">
<emphasis box="[916,1210,332,357]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">Flatovertex cyaneitibialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
herein as a junior synonym of 
<emphasis box="[291,562,367,392]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="550">
<taxonomicName box="[291,557,367,392]" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Pternoscirta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="caliginosa">Pternoscirta caliginosa</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
